RSS Syndications are the most popular way of following people and their
activities in the internet. We support syndications for various needs, like,

    * Follow changes to a wiki-page, or all wiki-pages under the project.
    * Follow changes to a ticket or all the tickets under the project.
    * Follow changes in singe review or all the reviews under the project.
    * Follow all the activites happening in the project.
    * Follow changes to a license or all the license pages.
    * Follow a user and their activities.
    * Follow all the activities happening in the site.
    * Follow revisions in version control.
